posts.name: Gralehaus
posts.note: Gralehaus is an eclectic nook in a Victorian house with seasonal breakfast and lunch bites, along with craft beers and coffee. You need to order the fried bologna sandwich with a fried egg on top or lamb and grits.

posts.name: Grind Burger Kitchen
posts.note: Grind Burger Kitchen serves burgers piled high with toppings served in a chill, modern space with craft beer on tap. The items to order are the Cubano with fries or the veggie burger.
